# Web bundle + Capacitor runtime config copied in by `cap sync` (from
# apps/android/dist) — build output, regenerated on every build, never
# hand-edited. Everything else cap sync writes (capacitor.settings.gradle,
# app/capacitor.build.gradle, capacitor-cordova-android-plugins/, res/xml/config.xml)
# IS committed — see docs/SETUP.md "Android native project structure".
app/src/main/assets/public/
app/src/main/assets/capacitor.config.json
app/src/main/assets/capacitor.plugins.json
